# Pro AI Server Rules

- Preserve existing CLI commands and flags unless the user explicitly approves a breaking change.
- Keep Android, ADB, Termux, Ollama, Continue, LAN, and Tailscale behavior visible and inspectable.
- Prefer USB localhost defaults unless the user explicitly chooses LAN or Tailscale exposure.
- Back up user configuration before overwriting it.
- Add or update tests for new behavior.
- Update docs when workflow commands or user-facing behavior changes.

